{
	"nodes": [
		{
			"id": "title",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1080,
			"y": -680,
			"width": 2760,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "# 诊断与系统修复模块\n\n先诊断，再定位责任层；先修正向模型，再决定是否需要护栏；最后同步机器契约、现有资产、可视化投影与验收。"
		},
		{
			"id": "scope-note",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1080,
			"y": -520,
			"width": 2760,
			"height": 90,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "# 读图口径\n\n左侧是诊断主流程；中部是新记录契约；底部是机器真相；右侧只做跳转导航。Canvas 是视觉投影，不替代 JSON / schema / validator。"
		},
		{
			"id": "failure-packet",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1080,
			"y": -330,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "1",
			"text": "# 1. Failure Packet\n\n冻结事故表现：当前文件、画布、命令、输出、用户纠正和上游输入。事故只是证据入口，不是根因问题。"
		},
		{
			"id": "evidence-tracks",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -540,
			"y": -330,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "4",
			"text": "# 2. 事故与根因问题\n\n分离 incident_manifestation、root_problem 和 system_regulation_target，再追下层证据链和上层原则链。"
		},
		{
			"id": "owner-and-class",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 0,
			"y": -330,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "# 3. 责任层与修复分类\n\n确定 owning repair layer。\n分类为 local_repair / system_upgrade / blocked_investigation。"
		},
		{
			"id": "positive-model-repair",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 540,
			"y": -330,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "# 4. 正向模型修复\n\n必填：positive_model_repair。\n先修模块边界、路由、registry、schema、dataflow、状态或生成机制。"
		},
		{
			"id": "constraint-decision",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1080,
			"y": -330,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "# 5. 约束决策\n\n必填：constraint_decision。\n只有当正向模型不足以防复发时，才补 forbidden_pattern 或 quality_gate。"
		},
		{
			"id": "surface-sync",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1080,
			"y": -70,
			"width": 420,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "# 6. 协同升级面\n\nsystem_upgrade 不能只改局部。先确认 failure_class，再扫描同类资产、兄弟模块、同层视图、route、schema、validator、review、Canvas 投影和 registry 关系。"
		},
		{
			"id": "validation",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -480,
			"y": -70,
			"width": 420,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "# 7. 校验\n\n运行相关 validator。校验通过只是证据，不等于诊断接受；接受必须回到原 failure packet。"
		},
		{
			"id": "acceptance",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 120,
			"y": -70,
			"width": 420,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "3",
			"text": "# 8. Diagnosis Acceptance\n\n验收不仅看目标对象是否修好；如果用户纠正暴露漏诊、误判或提前闭环，必须进入诊断自审。"
		},
		{
			"id": "visual-projection-sync",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 720,
			"y": -70,
			"width": 720,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "# 9. 可视化投影同步\n\n如果升级模块有 Canvas 覆盖，必须更新对应画布、view graph、support bindings / relations，或登记不需要更新的理由。"
		},
		{
			"id": "contract-band",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1080,
			"y": 170,
			"width": 2760,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "# 当前诊断记录契约\n\n机器记录以 positive_model_repair + constraint_decision 为主；旧字段只作为历史兼容或明确护栏时的补充。"
		},
		{
			"id": "required-contract",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1080,
			"y": 290,
			"width": 600,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "# 必填字段\n\nincident_manifestation / root_problem / system_regulation_target / evidence tracks / owning_repair_layer / positive_model_repair / constraint_decision / generalization_scan"
		},
		{
			"id": "optional-guardrail",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -360,
			"y": 290,
			"width": 600,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "# 可选护栏字段\n\npositive_rule / forbidden_pattern / quality_gate 仅用于历史记录或明确需要硬护栏时。它们不再强迫每个诊断都生成禁令。"
		},
		{
			"id": "closed-loop-note",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 360,
			"y": 290,
			"width": 720,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "5",
			"text": "# 本次闭环修复点\n\n新增 OR 借鉴层：先用层级矩阵判断责任层，再由失败学习循环决定是否生成 postmortem、proposal、regression guard 和 promotion decision。"
		},
		{
			"id": "machine-truth-band",
			"type": "text",
			"x": -1080,
			"y": 500,
			"width": 2760,
			"height": 80,
			"color": "6",
			"text": "# 机器真相\n\n诊断控制器、层级矩阵、失败学习循环、问题队列、schema 和 validator 决定系统行为；Canvas 只做可读入口和结构投影。"
		},
		{
			"id": "diagnostic-system-file",
			"type": "file",
