		},
		{
			"id": "failure-learning-loop",
			"type": "text",
			"x": 1120,
			"y": 290,
			"width": 560,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "2",
			"text": "# 10. 失败学习循环\n\n高风险或重复问题才进入。借鉴 OR：postmortem -> proposal -> sandbox/dry-run -> regression guard -> promotion decision。只生成受控改进对象，不自动晋升规则或记忆。"
		},
